VarianceTest[{x, y}, 1, \"HypothesisTestData\"][\"TestDataTable\"]\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"573234a8-3c9f-4ee6-b002-65bc50843f49"],

Cell["\<\
m = Length[x]; n = Length[y]; dist = FRatioDistribution[m - 1, n - 1];
F = Variance[x]/Variance[y]/r; f = F /. r -> 1;
c = CDF[dist][f];
{f, 2 Min[c, 1 - c]} // N\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"07839869-ed08-4070-b2c5-a53f218ae439"],

Cell["\<\
